{"head":{"description":"color-no-invalid-hex Disallow invalid hex colors. 禁止使用无效的十六进制颜色。 Longhand hex colors can be either 6 or 8 (with alpha channel) hexadecimal…","title":"color-no-invalid-hex"},"body":"<h1 id=\"color-no-invalid-hex\"><a href=\"#color-no-invalid-hex\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>color-no-invalid-hex</h1>\n<p>Disallow invalid hex colors.</p>\n<p>禁止使用无效的十六进制颜色。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: #y3 }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**        ↑\n * These hex colors */</span></code></pre>\n<p>Longhand hex colors can be either 6 or 8 (with alpha channel) hexadecimal characters. And their shorthand variants are 3 and 4 characters respectively.</p>\n<p>十六进制颜色普通写法可以是 6 或 8（带有 alpha 通道）个十六进制字符。它们对应的简写形式分别为 3 和 4个字符。</p>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Options</h2>\n<h3 id=\"true\"><a href=\"#true\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>true</code></h3>\n<p>The following patterns are considered warnings:</p>\n<p>以下模式被认为是个警告：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#00</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#fff1a</span>z; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#12345aa</span>; }</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered warnings:</p>\n<p>以下模式正常：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#000</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#000f</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#fff1a0</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">color</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">#123450aa</span>; }</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/color-no-invalid-hex.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/color-no-invalid-hex/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/color-no-invalid-hex/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/color-no-invalid-hex/index.html.1f6277827b4d8cffe6cd4158ae222d5b.json"}